[2025-02-19T09:01Z] Pre-aggregated summary received: 47,320 requests across 6 endpoint groups
[2025-02-19T09:02Z] Prior finding (08:00 window): eu-west-1 p99 elevated on /v3/payments (712 ms, within SLO)
###END:SESSION_STATE###

###ICS:TASK_PAYLOAD###
Analyse the 08:00–09:00 UTC summary for SLO compliance.

Pre-aggregated summary:
  endpoint_group        region       count   p50_ms  p95_ms  p99_ms  error_rate
  /v3/payments          us-east-1    18,441  98      310     620     0.12%
  /v3/payments          eu-west-1     9,204  114     388     941     0.31%
  /v3/reconciliation    us-east-1     6,112  240     980    2,140    0.08%
  /v3/webhooks          us-east-1     7,830  88      270     560     1.44%
  /v3/webhooks          eu-west-1     3,901  101     310     688     1.67%
  /v3/admin             us-east-1     1,832  45       90     180     0.00%

Identify any SLO breaches, flag whether the eu-west-1 /v3/payments elevation is worsening
relative to the prior window, and note whether the /v3/webhooks error rate warrants escalation.
###END:TASK_PAYLOAD###

###ICS:OUTPUT_CONTRACT###
format:     JSON
schema: {
  "window": "string",
  "endpoint_verdicts": [
    {
      "endpoint_group":  "string",
      "region":          "string",
      "slo_verdict":     "PASS" | "BREACH" | "DEGRADED",
      "breach_level":    "CRITICAL" | "HIGH" | "MEDIUM" | null,
      "p99_ms":          "number",
      "slo_p99_ms":      "number",
      "notes":           "string"
    }
  ],
  "region_variance_flagged": "boolean",
  "escalation_required":     "boolean",
  "escalation_reason":       "string | null"
}
variance:   "breach_level" MUST be null when "slo_verdict" is PASS;
            "breach_level" MUST be "CRITICAL" for any /v3/payments* p99 breach;
            "escalation_reason" MUST be null when "escalation_required" is false;
            /v3/admin results MUST NOT appear in "endpoint_verdicts"
on_failure: Return { "status": "error", "reason": "<single-sentence description>" }
###END:OUTPUT_CONTRACT###
